"> <b>Your subscription has been paused for one month, until #suspension_date#.</b> <span>If you’d like to resume it earlier, please <a id="js-suspended-banner-help" class="fcst-cta-button fcst-cta-button--suspended" href="https://www.lemonde.fr/faq/?question=je-souhaite-contacter-le-service-client-du-monde">contact our customer service team</a>.</span> </span> </div> <div class="fcst-close fcst-close--suspended"></div> </div> </div>  </div>            <main role="main" class="main LeMondeMain  main--free    ">         <div id="dfp-habillage" class="dfp-slot dfp__slot dfp__slot--habillage" data-format="habillage" aria-hidden="true"></div> <div class="dfp__container"><div id="banniere_haute" class="dfp-slot dfp__slot dfp__slot--banniere dfp__slot--banniere-haute adm-ad-loading" data-format="banniere_haute" aria-hidden="true"><div class="loader"></div></div></div>           <div id="habillagepub">          <section class="zone zone--homepage zone--highlight">   <section class="area area--main old__area-main-wide"> <div class="article article--main" data-zone="highlight"> <div class="lmd-link-clickarea">          <span id="zone1-premium-92771" class="icon__premium icon--outside"><span class="sr-only">Subscribers only</span></span><h1 class="article__title"><a href="https://www.lemonde.fr/en/opinion/article/2026/03/17/france-s-national-political-crisis-is-taking-root-locally_6751535_23.html" class="lmd-link-clickarea__link" aria-describedby="zone1-premium-92771"> <p class="article__title-label">France's national political crisis is taking root locally</p> </a> </h1>   <div class="article__media-container"> <picture class="article__media"> <source media="(min-width: 576px) and (max-width: 1023px)" srcset=" https://img.lemde.fr/2026/03/16/655/0/7859/3929/1400/700/75/0/2389956_upload-1-9xnngeclaxrd-amsellem-municipales-052.jpg 700w, https://img.lemde.fr/2026/03/16/655/0/7859/3929/1600/800/75/0/2389956_upload-1-9xnngeclaxrd-amsellem-municipales-052.jpg 800w, https://img.lemde.fr/2026/03/16/655/0/7859/3929/1800/900/75/0/2389956_upload-1-9xnngeclaxrd-amsellem-municipales-052.jpg 900w" sizes="664px"> <source media="(min-width: 1024px)" srcset=" https://img.lemde.fr/2026/03/16/655/0/7859/3929/1400/700/75/0/2389956_upload-1-9xnngeclaxrd-amsellem-municipales-052.jpg 700w, https://img.lemde.fr/2026/03/16/655/0/7859/3929/1600/800/75/0/2389956_upload-1-9xnngeclaxrd-amsellem-municipales-052.jpg 800w, https://img.lemde.fr/2026/03/16/655/0/7859/3929/1800/900/75/0/2389956_upload-1-9xnngeclaxrd-amsellem-municipales-052.jpg 900w" sizes="644px"> <source srcset=" https://img.lemde.fr/2026/03/16/0/0/7858/5239/800/533/75/0/2389956_upload-1-9xnngeclaxrd-amsellem-municipales-052.jpg 400w, https://img.lemde.fr/2026/03/16/0/0/7858/5239/1000/666/75/0/2389956_upload-1-9xnngeclaxrd-amsellem-municipales-052.jpg 500w, https://img.lemde.fr/2026/03/16/0/0/7858/5239/1200/800/75/0/2389956_upload-1-9xnngeclaxrd-amsellem-municipales-052.jpg 600w, https://img.lemde.fr/2026/03/16/0/0/7858/5239/1400/933/75/0/2389956_upload-1-9xnngeclaxrd-amsellem-municipales-052.jpg 700w, https://img.lemde.fr/2026/03/16/0/0/7858/5239/1600/1066/75/0/2389956_upload-1-9xnngeclaxrd-amsellem-municipales-052.jpg 800w, https://img.lemde.fr/2026/03/16/0/0/7858/5239/1800/1200/75/0/2389956_upload-1-9xnngeclaxrd-amsellem-municipales-052.jpg 900w"> <img src="https://img.lemde.fr/2026/03/16/0/0/7858/5239/600/400/75/0/2389956_upload-1-9xnngeclaxrd-amsellem-municipales-052.jpg" alt="At a polling station in Lyon, March 15, 2026." width="3" height="2"> <noscript> <img src="https://img.lemde.fr/2026/03/16/0/0/7858/5239/600/400/75/0/2389956_upload-1-9xnngeclaxrd-amsellem-municipales-052.jpg" alt="At a polling station in Lyon, March 15, 2026." width="3" height="2"> </noscript> </picture>    </div>   <div class="article__media-credit article__media-credit--une"> BRUNO AMSELLEM/DIVERGENCE FOR Le Monde </div>   <p class="article__desc">The first round of the municipal elections, marked by low turnout and fragmented landscapes in big cities, confirms the depth of France's political crisis, writes Le Monde columnist Françoise Fressoz.</p>  </div> <ul class="article__related old__article-related-container">  <li><span id="zone1-highlight-related-premium-92742-0" class="icon__premium"> <span class="sr-only">Subscribers only</span> </span><a href="https://www.lemonde.fr/en/les-decodeurs/article/2026/03/17/2026-municipal-elections-five-key-takeaways-from-the-first-round_6751512_8.html" aria-describedby="zone1-highlight-related-premium-92742-0"data-zone="highlight highlight_appui">Five takeaways from the first round of French local elections </a> </li>   <li><span id="zone1-highlight-related-premium-92791-1" class="icon__premium"> <span class="sr-only">Subscribers only</span> </span><a href="https://www.lemonde.fr/en/politics/article/2026/03/18/paris-municipal-elections-three-candidates-head-to-the-second-round-following-sarah-knafo-s-withdrawal_6751543_5.html" aria-describedby="zone1-highlight-related-premium-92791-1"data-zone="highlight highlight_appui">Paris municipal elections: Three candidates head to the second round following Sarah Knafo's withdrawal </a> </li>   <li><span id="zone1-highlight-related-premium-92763-2" class="icon__premium"> <span class="sr-only">Subscribers only</span> </span><a href="https://www.lemonde.fr/en/politics/article/2026/03/17/french-municipal-elections-socialists-and-lfi-set-aside-differences-to-strike-local-deals_6751527_5.html" aria-describedby="zone1-highlight-related-premium-92763-2"data-zone="highlight highlight_appui">French municipal elections: Socialists and LFI set aside differences to strike local deals </a> </li> </ul> </div> </section>    <section class="area area--runner">            <div class="article article--runner old__article-runner" data-zone="titles title_4_5_6">    <div class="lmd-link-clickarea"> <div class="article__media-container "> <picture class="article__media article__media--with-credit">   <img data-srcset="https://img.lemde.fr/2026/03/05/0/0/1500/1000/398/265/75/0/32e42c9_upload-1-6kdnma8rsdxb-frame-1463.jpg 398w, https://img.lemde.fr/2026/03/05/0/0/1500/1000/228/152/75/0/32e42c9_upload-1-6kdnma8rsdxb-frame-1463.jpg 228w, https://img.lemde.fr/2026/03/05/0/0/1500/1000/114/76/75/0/32e42c9_upload-1-6kdnma8rsdxb-frame-1463.jpg 114w" data-src="https://img.lemde.fr/2026/03/05/0/0/1500/1000/398/265/75/0/32e42c9_upload-1-6kdnma8rsdxb-frame-1463.jpg" data-sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 114px, 199px" alt="" width="199" height="132" >  <noscript><img src="https://img.lemde.fr/2026/03/05/0/0/1500/1000/252/168/75/0/32e42c9_upload-1-6kdnma8rsdxb-frame-1463.jpg" alt="" width="252" height="168"></noscript>  </picture>  </div>   <div class="article__media-credit article__media-credit--only-desktop"> « Le Monde » </div>  <span id="premium-92792" class="icon__premium icon--outside-simple"><span class="sr-only">Subscribers only</span></span><a class="lmd-link-clickarea__link" href="https://www.lemonde.fr/en/opinion/article/2026/03/18/war-in-iran-spain-s-resolve-stands-in-stark-contrast-to-france-s-stance-which-seems-more-accepting-of-us-israeli-strikes_6751546_23.html" aria-describedby="premium-92792"> <p class="article__title">War in Iran: 'Spain's resolve stands in stark contrast to France's stance, which seems more accepting of US-Israeli strikes'</p> </a>   <p class="article__desc">Historian Laurence Badel analyzes the reasons behind the Spanish government's 'no to war' position and the impact of this decision on the European diplomatic landscape.</p>    </div>  </div>      <div class="article article--runner old__article-runner" data-zone="titles title_4_5_6">    <div class="lmd-link-clickarea"> <div class="article__media-container "> <picture class="article__media article__media--with-credit">   <img data-srcset="https://img.lemde.fr/2026/03/01/0/0/3078/2052/398/265/75/0/e812514_ftp-1-hw4uk8vmhyw7-2026-03-01t081905z-1184975730-rc2l5ba6mv6d-rtrmadp-3-iran-crisis-larijani.JPG 398w, https://img.lemde.fr/2026/03/01/0/0/3078/2052/228/152/75/0/e812514_ftp-1-hw4uk8vmhyw7-2026-03-01t081905z-1184975730-rc2l5ba6mv6d-rtrmadp-3-iran-crisis-larijani.JPG 228w, https://img.lemde.fr/2026/03/01/0/0/3078/2052/114/76/75/0/e812514_ftp-1-hw4uk8vmhyw7-2026-03-01t081905z-1184975730-rc2l5ba6mv6d-rtrmadp-3-iran-crisis-larijani.JPG 114w" data-src="https://img.lemde.fr/2026/03/01/0/0/3078/2052/398/265/75/0/e812514_ftp-1-hw4uk8vmhyw7-2026-03-01t081905z-1184975730-rc2l5ba6mv6d-rtrmadp-3-iran-crisis-larijani.JPG" data-sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 114px, 199px" alt="Ali Larijani in Beirut, Lebanon, November 15, 2024." width="199" height="132" >  <noscript><img src="https://img.lemde.fr/2026/03/01/0/0/3078/2052/252/168/75/0/e812514_ftp-1-hw4uk8vmhyw7-2026-03-01t081905z-1184975730-rc2l5ba6mv6d-rtrmadp-3-iran-crisis-larijani.JPG" alt="Ali Larijani in Beirut, Lebanon, November 15, 2024." width="252" height="168"></noscript>  </picture>  </div>   <div class="article__media-credit article__media-credit--only-desktop"> Thaier Al-Sudani / REUTERS </div>  <a class="lmd-link-clickarea__link" href="https://www.lemonde.fr/en/middle-east-crisis/article/2026/03/17/israel-says-iran-s-security-chief-ali-larijani-killed-in-strike_6751524_368.html"> <p class="article__title">Iran confirms death of security chief Larijani</p> </a>   <p class="article__desc">Iran's Supreme National Security Council confirmed the death of 'Martyr Dr. Ali Larijani,' stating that his son and his bodyguards died with him, after Israel announced earlier on Tuesday it had killed him in an air strike.</p>    </div>  </div>      <div class="article article--runner old__article-runner" data-zone="titles title_4_5_6">    <div class="lmd-link-clickarea"> <div class="article__media-container "> <picture class="article__media article__media--with-credit">   <img data-srcset="https://img.lemde.fr/2026/03/17/0/0/4873/3249/398/265/75/0/0044b62_ftp-1-nxuuhsud2upy-c3d57eb8720e401d86470ec0748076cd-0-c6935e7785c44387abd56cff4e66449b.jpg 39