5dec459_upload-1-dur2ez0ancas-frame-1353.jpg 355w" data-sizes="(min-width: 1024px) 355px, 664px" alt="" width="664" height="443" > <noscript> <img src="https://img.lemde.fr/2026/01/06/0/0/3000/2000/664/442/75/0/5dec459_upload-1-dur2ez0ancas-frame-1353.jpg" alt=""> </noscript> </picture> </div>  <div class="article__wrapper">  <p class="article__type">News</p>  <p class="article__byline"> Pierre Breteau,  Manon Romain and  Raphaëlle Aubert</p> <p class="article__title article__title--inline">2026 municipal elections: See the first-round results on our map</p>  <p class="article__desc">Follow the 2026 municipal elections' first-round results in real time with our interactive map, and see which lists are in the lead and which mayors have been directly elected.</p>  </div>  </a>  </div>    <div class="article article--featured old__article-square" data-zone="selection">  <a href="https://www.lemonde.fr/en/france/article/2026/03/16/french-court-examines-yazidi-genocide-for-first-time-in-trial-of-jihadist_6751491_7.html">  <div class="article__media-container"> <picture class="article__media"> <img data-src="https://img.lemde.fr/2026/03/14/0/0/4500/3000/664/442/75/0/e400dd1_upload-1-t7wmvwu8mr5j-lgeai-yezidis-08-2021-40.jpg" data-srcset="https://img.lemde.fr/2026/03/14/0/0/4500/3000/1328/885/45/0/e400dd1_upload-1-t7wmvwu8mr5j-lgeai-yezidis-08-2021-40.jpg 1328w, https://img.lemde.fr/2026/03/14/0/0/4500/3000/664/442/75/0/e400dd1_upload-1-t7wmvwu8mr5j-lgeai-yezidis-08-2021-40.jpg 664w, https://img.lemde.fr/2026/03/14/0/0/4500/3000/355/236/75/0/e400dd1_upload-1-t7wmvwu8mr5j-lgeai-yezidis-08-2021-40.jpg 355w" data-sizes="(min-width: 1024px) 355px, 664px" alt="In Kocho, Iraq, August 3, 2021, where Yazidis murdered by the Islamic State group were buried in a mass grave." width="664" height="443" > <noscript> <img src="https://img.lemde.fr/2026/03/14/0/0/4500/3000/664/442/75/0/e400dd1_upload-1-t7wmvwu8mr5j-lgeai-yezidis-08-2021-40.jpg" alt="In Kocho, Iraq, August 3, 2021, where Yazidis murdered by the Islamic State group were buried in a mass grave."> </noscript> </picture> </div>  <div class="article__wrapper">  <p class="article__type">In Depth</p>  <p class="article__byline"> Soren Seelow</p> <span class="icon__premium"><span class="sr-only">Subscribers only</span></span><p class="article__title article__title--inline">French court examines Yazidi genocide for first time in trial of jihadist</p>  <p class="article__desc">Sabri Essid is being tried in absentia, charged with 'genocide,' a first in France. Two women from the Iraqi minority will testify, recounting how they were enslaved.</p>  </div>  <p class="article__footer-info">4 min read </p>  </a>  </div>    <div class="article article--featured old__article-square" data-zone="selection">  <a href="https://www.lemonde.fr/en/international/article/2026/03/17/serbia-emerges-as-main-hub-for-russian-destabilization-operations-in-europe_6751510_4.html">  <div class="article__media-container"> <picture class="article__media"> <img data-src="https://img.lemde.fr/2026/03/13/0/210/2265/1510/664/442/75/0/7883323_upload-1-3fjchhy22wha-capture-d-e-cran-2026-03-12-a-7-02-08-pm.png" data-srcset="https://img.lemde.fr/2026/03/13/0/210/2265/1510/1328/885/45/0/7883323_upload-1-3fjchhy22wha-capture-d-e-cran-2026-03-12-a-7-02-08-pm.png 1328w, https://img.lemde.fr/2026/03/13/0/210/2265/1510/664/442/75/0/7883323_upload-1-3fjchhy22wha-capture-d-e-cran-2026-03-12-a-7-02-08-pm.png 664w, https://img.lemde.fr/2026/03/13/0/210/2265/1510/355/236/75/0/7883323_upload-1-3fjchhy22wha-capture-d-e-cran-2026-03-12-a-7-02-08-pm.png 355w" data-sizes="(min-width: 1024px) 355px, 664px" alt="Screenshot from a video posted on October 5, 2020, on the YouTube channel Light2tube, showing the town of Velika Plana, Serbia." width="664" height="443" > <noscript> <img src="https://img.lemde.fr/2026/03/13/0/210/2265/1510/664/442/75/0/7883323_upload-1-3fjchhy22wha-capture-d-e-cran-2026-03-12-a-7-02-08-pm.png" alt="Screenshot from a video posted on October 5, 2020, on the YouTube channel Light2tube, showing the town of Velika Plana, Serbia."> </noscript> </picture> </div>  <div class="article__wrapper">  <p class="article__type">Letter from...</p>  <p class="article__byline"> Jean-Baptiste Chastand</p> <span class="icon__premium"><span class="sr-only">Subscribers only</span></span><p class="article__title article__title--inline">Serbia emerges as main hub for Russian destabilization operations in Europe</p>  <p class="article__desc">Three Serbian nationals were sentenced at the end of December 2025 for placing pig heads in front of mosques in the Paris region – an operation explicitly linked to the Kremlin.</p>  </div>  <p class="article__footer-info">3 min read </p>  </a>  </div>   </div>                     <div class="area area--section old__area old__area--section"> <h4 class="area__title old__area-title">  <a href="/en/opinion/">Opinion</a>  </h4>   <div class="article article--opinion old__article-square" data-zone="ideas"> <a href="https://www.lemonde.fr/en/opinion/article/2026/03/17/for-donald-trump-the-middle-east-war-is-a-way-to-avenge-the-united-states-past-military-traumas_6751507_23.html">  <div class="article__type">Op-Ed</div> <span class="icon__premium icon--outside"><span class="sr-only">Subscribe</span></span><p class="article__title">'For Trump, the Middle East war is a way to avenge the United States' past military traumas'</p>   <div class="article__author">  <div> <div class="article__author-name">Marie-Cécile Naves</div> <div class="article__author-desc">political scientist</div> </div> </div>  </a> </div>    <div class="article article--opinion old__article-square" data-zone="ideas"> <a href="https://www.lemonde.fr/en/opinion/article/2026/03/17/europeans-get-a-downgraded-version-of-ai-which-can-only-delay-their-adaptation_6751537_23.html">  <div class="article__type">Column</div> <span class="icon__premium icon--outside"><span class="sr-only">Subscribe</span></span><p class